      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STA[TES] GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO: DIRECTOR, FBI",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "DATE: 4/28/53",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "FROM: SAC, SAN JUAN (65-330)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "SUBJECT: UNIDENTIFIED FLYING OBJECT OBSERVED",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "11:30 AM, APRIL 8, 1953, FORT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "BUCHANAN, PUERTO RICO;",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "On 4/27/53 a report was received from Major [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Wing Intelligence Officer, Ramey Air Force Base, Puerto Rico.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "The substance of this report is as follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Five persons observed an unidentified flying object at 11:30",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "AM on 4/8/53 at Fort Buchanan, Puerto Rico. Statements were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "taken from all of the witnesses, among whom were three Captains",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "and a Sergeant of the U. S. Army, as well as a civilian. They",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "described the object as a bright star or a bright ball of fire",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "at a great height, and it was moving rapidly at the time it was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "observed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "All of the witnesses observed one RB 36 aircraft which had been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "flying in the area at the time of the sighting of this unidenti-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "fied object. The Wing Intelligence Officer reported that there",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "were two RB 36 aircraft in the area at this time. These aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "were reported to be flying at 12,000 and 21,000 feet respectively.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "None of the persons from whom statements were taken were able to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "accurately describe the object, other than by the statements set",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "forth above.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "This matter is being reported to the Bureau for information",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "purposes.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "CLOSED.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
